snippet.title: K.K. INTERNET ("Welcome to the Internet" by Bo Burnham)
snippet.description:
CONTENT WARNING: This is total whiplash from what I usually post. Just wanna let you know, there are some crude words and some heavy topics in this song.

Bo has now officially been sung on this channel. Here's a K.K. Slider cover of Welcome to the Internet from Bo Burnham's special "Inside", in honor of the Inside Outtakes releasing a couple days ago. The whole song is remade with Animal Crossing instruments, and I found that there was also a fart in the soundfont for some reason. You're welcome.

We also hit 1k subs, which is absolutely stupid crazy. Thanks a ton for each and every one of you for watching and sticking around over the years, and I apologize if this video is a bit too weird for a lot of you new viewers out there. Nonetheless, I hope you like it. This song, along with the whole album, has been looping in my head ever since it released a year or two ago.
